00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:04.960
 And the guy went, how much?

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:06.440
 And apparently, he was a little bit too much.

00:07:06.440 --> 00:07:08.480
 And so this guy had to go and get some other donors.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:10.760
 But it was from that moment that this started.

00:07:10.760 --> 00:07:11.720
 Is that right, Mary?

00:07:11.720 --> 00:07:14.200
 - Yeah, there were Moscow around that time.

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:18.320
 They had this clinic, and I'm not gonna attempt to pronounce it,

00:07:18.320 --> 00:07:19.360
 'cause it's Russian-y.

00:07:19.360 --> 00:07:20.800
 (laughing)

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:23.960
 But it was a cadaver blood clinic.

00:07:23.960 --> 00:07:27.760
 So all of the accidents, all the, you know, emergency trauma,

00:07:27.760 --> 00:07:29.880
 et cetera, deaths, sudden deaths.

