 a blood transfusion might have killed him quicker

00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:20.840
 as a result of the injuries he sustained,

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:21.840
 but he retired from it.

00:09:21.840 --> 00:09:23.160
 - But it made a nice story.

00:09:23.160 --> 00:09:24.400
 - Yes, exactly.

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:27.360
 - Which I was perpetuating.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.240
 (laughing)

